Australia named the following 30-man
preliminary squad for the 2011 Cricket World Cup to be staged
Feb. 19-April 2 in India, Sri Lanka and Bangladesh. The final
15-man roster must be submitted by Jan. 19.  Ricky Ponting (captain), Michael Clarke (vice-captain),
Doug Bollinger, Dan Christian, Xavier Doherty, Callum Ferguson,
Brad Haddin, Ryan Harris, John Hastings, Nathan Hauritz, Brad
Hodge, James Hopes, David Hussey, Mike Hussey, Mitchell Johnson,
